de.tr7zw.changeme.nbtapi

Class NBTEntity

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.tr7zw.changeme.nbtapi.NBTCompound
      • de.tr7zw.changeme.nbtapi.NBTEntity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ReadableNBT, ReadWriteNBT

    public class NBTEntity
extends NBTCompound
    NBT class to access vanilla tags from Entities. Entities don't support custom tags. Use the NBTInjector for custom tags. Changes will be instantly applied to the Entity, use the merge method to do many things at once.
    Author:
    tr7zw
